column16: David Wright pops out to catcher Yadier Molina in foul territory.
Luis Castillo flies out to left fielder Kyle Lohse.
Jose Reyes out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Ryan Ludwick.   Angel Pagan scores.
Mike Jacobs singles on a line drive to right fielder Allen Craig.   Angel Pagan to 3rd.
Angel Pagan singles on a soft ground ball to pitcher Joe Mather.
Raul Valdes grounds out, first baseman Albert Pujols to pitcher Joe Mather.
Joe Mather intentionally walks Henry Blanco.   David Wright to 3rd.    Jason Bay to 2nd.
Jeff Francoeur out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Kyle Lohse.   Jose Reyes scores.
Jason Bay hit by pitch.    Jose Reyes to 3rd.    David Wright to 2nd.
Joe Mather intentionally walks David Wright.
Luis Castillo out on a sacrifice bunt, third baseman Felipe Lopez to first baseman Albert Pujols.   Jose Reyes to 2nd.
